item.title:
Emma Stone on attending Taylor Swift’s #ErasTour:
“I’ve known her since we were 17 and 18… She blows my mind. I mean, the amount of sheer stamina to do three and a half hours & perform 44 songs & to maintain the extreme energy of the audience—I’ve never seen anything like it.”
